## Additional Terms for Academic Use

This software is specifically designed for academic portfolios and educational purposes.

When using this software for your academic portfolio:
1. You are free to customize and modify the code for your personal use
2. Please provide attribution by keeping a link to the original repository
3. If you make improvements, consider contributing back to the community

For commercial use beyond personal academic portfolios, please contact the maintainers.
